# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Frontend Environment Variables
# Copy to .env.development.local for local development
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Self-hosting (see docs/self-hosting.md) ──────────────────
# These control where the frontend sends API calls and loads assets.
# In prod builds: baked into the bundle at build time.
# Defaults point to the public EV 2090 deployment.

# API base URL — your game worker (chat, forge, economy)
# Default: https://ws.ev2090.com
# Self-hosted: set to your worker domain (e.g., https://yourdomain.com)
# VITE_API_URL=https://yourdomain.com

# Asset base URL — 3D ship models and textures (served from R2)
# Default: https://ws.ev2090.com/api/forge/asset
# Self-hosted: set to your worker domain (models are fetched from VITE_API_URL automatically)
# VITE_ASSET_URL=https://yourdomain.com/api/forge/asset

# CDN base URL — static assets (images, audio)
# Default: https://cdn.ev2090.com
# Self-hosted: set to your domain or leave unset to use the API worker's asset endpoint
# VITE_CDN_URL=https://yourdomain.com

# ── Dev proxy target ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Where the Vite dev proxy sends /api/* requests (dev mode only).
# Default: https://ws.ev2090.com (production) or http://127.0.0.1:8787 (devworker mode)
# VITE_API_PROXY_TARGET=http://localhost:8787

# ── Ship Forge ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Admin API key (optional — only needed for forge admin access)
# VITE_FORGE_API_KEY=your_forge_api_key_here
